IAeMessageDataStrategyMatcher
public class AeBPWSMessageDataStrategyMatcher
extends AeBaseMessageDataStrategyMatcher

Contains the valid strategy patterns for BPEL4WS 1.1 The only valid message data consumer or producer strategy for 1.1 is the message-variable strategy. The base class provides this strategy so there's really nothing here.
